SET Process TO $'''Checking OBS'''
IF (System.IfProcess.ProcessIsNotRunning ProcessName: $'''obs64''') THEN
    SET Process TO $'''Starting OBS'''
    Cmd.Open.Open Directory: VirtualCameraPath Session=> CmdSession
        ON ERROR

        END
    Cmd.Write Session: CmdSession Command: $'''start /d \"%VirtualCameraPath%\" obs64.exe''' SendEnter: True
        ON ERROR

        END
    Cmd.Close Session: CmdSession
    WAIT 15
END
SET Process TO $'''Pressing the button'''
UIAutomation.PressButton Button: appmask['Window \'安全模式\'']['Button \'正常运行\''] Simulate: False
    ON ERROR

    END
UIAutomation.SetCheckboxState Checkbox: appmask['Window \'OBS 30.1.2 - 配置文件: 未命名 - 场景: 未命名\'']['Check Box \'启动虚拟摄像机\''] CheckboxState: UIAutomation.CheckboxState.Checked
    ON ERROR

    END
SET Process TO $'''Sending Win + D'''
MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{LWin}({D})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
SET Process TO $'''Checking Tencent Meeting App'''
IF (System.IfProcess.ProcessIsNotRunning ProcessName: $'''wemeetapp''') THEN
    SET Process TO $'''Starting Tencent Meeting App'''
    System.RunApplication.RunApplication ApplicationPath: MeetingPath WindowStyle: System.ProcessWindowStyle.Normal ProcessId=> AppProcessId
        ON ERROR

        END
    WAIT 15
END
SET Process TO $'''Pressing button'''
MouseAndKeyboard.MoveMouseToImage.ClickImage Images: [imgrepo['Start'], imgrepo['Cancel']] SearchForImageOn: MouseAndKeyboard.SearchTarget.EntireScreen MousePositionOnImage: MouseAndKeyboard.PositionOnImage.MiddleCenter OffsetX: 0 OffsetY: 0 Tolerance: 10 MovementStyle: MouseAndKeyboard.MovementStyle.Instant Occurence: 1 Timeout: 5 ClickType: MouseAndKeyboard.ClickType.LeftClick SecondsBeforeClick: 0 SearchAlgorithm: MouseAndKeyboard.ImageFinderAlgorithm.Legacy X=> X Y=> Y
    ON ERROR

    END
SET Process TO $'''Pressing button \"Enter The Meeting\"'''
MouseAndKeyboard.MoveMouseToImage.ClickImage Images: [imgrepo['Start'], imgrepo['Enter']] SearchForImageOn: MouseAndKeyboard.SearchTarget.EntireScreen MousePositionOnImage: MouseAndKeyboard.PositionOnImage.MiddleCenter OffsetX: 0 OffsetY: 0 Tolerance: 10 MovementStyle: MouseAndKeyboard.MovementStyle.Instant Occurence: 1 Timeout: 5 ClickType: MouseAndKeyboard.ClickType.LeftClick SecondsBeforeClick: 0 SearchAlgorithm: MouseAndKeyboard.ImageFinderAlgorithm.Legacy X=> X Y=> Y
    ON ERROR

    END
SET Process TO $'''Filling textbox'''
UIAutomation.PopulateTextField.PopulateTextField TextField: appmask['Window \'加入会议\'']['Edit \'请输入会议号\''] Text: ID Mode: UIAutomation.PopulateTextMode.Replace ClickType: UIAutomation.PopulateMouseClickType.SingleClick
    ON ERROR

    END
SET Process TO $'''Pressing button \"Enter The Meeting\"'''
UIAutomation.PressButton Button: appmask['Window \'加入会议\'']['Button \'加入会议\''] Simulate: False
    ON ERROR

    END
SET Process TO $'''Done'''
WAIT 5
SET Process TO $'''Letting the window to the top'''
UIAutomation.Click.Click Element: appmask['Window \'会中主窗口\'']['Group \'QWidget\''] ClickType: UIAutomation.ClickType.LeftClick MousePositionRelativeToElement: UIAutomation.RectangleEdgePoint.MiddleCenter OffsetX: -113 OffsetY: -3
    ON ERROR

    END
SET Process TO $'''Checking image - audio'''
IF (UIAutomation.IfImage.ExistsOnScreen Images: [imgrepo['AudioOpen']] FindAllImages: False Tolerance: 10 SearchAlgorithm: UIAutomation.ImageFinderAlgorithm.Legacy) THEN
    SET Process TO $'''Closing audio'''
    UIAutomation.Click.Click Element: appmask['Window \'会中主窗口\'']['Group \'QWidget\''] ClickType: UIAutomation.ClickType.LeftClick MousePositionRelativeToElement: UIAutomation.RectangleEdgePoint.MiddleCenter OffsetX: -113 OffsetY: -3
        ON ERROR

        END
    @@source: 'Recorder'
MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: '{LMenu}({M})'
END
SET Process TO $'''Checking image - video'''
IF (UIAutomation.IfImage.ExistsOnScreen Images: [imgrepo['AudioClose'], imgrepo['CameraClose'], imgrepo['CameraOpen']] FindAllImages: False Tolerance: 10 SearchAlgorithm: UIAutomation.ImageFinderAlgorithm.Legacy) THEN
    SET Process TO $'''Opening video'''
    UIAutomation.Click.Click Element: appmask['Window \'会中主窗口\'']['Group \'QWidget\''] ClickType: UIAutomation.ClickType.LeftClick MousePositionRelativeToElement: UIAutomation.RectangleEdgePoint.MiddleCenter OffsetX: -113 OffsetY: -3
        ON ERROR

        END
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{LMenu}({V})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
END
SET Process TO $'''Done'''
WAIT 25
